[SN]TITLE[SN]
Probe after Aberdeen cinema fight during T2 Trainspotting

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Inquiries are ongoing into an alleged assault which took place during a screening of T2 Trainspotting an Aberdeen cinema.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident is believed to have taken place at 21:15 on Thursday at the Belmont Filmhouse.
It is understood the alleged assault happened after a man answered his phone during the film.
A Police Scotland spokesman said they have yet to trace the people involved.
